title: Curiosity Call Update: Did She Ever Reunite With Her College Sweetheart?
description:
Last year, we helped our listener Chelsea with a "Curiosity Call". Her college sweetheart abruptly broke up with her before they graduated. She was heartbroken and never knew why ended things. 
We reached out to him for answers. Then the two confessed they still have feelings for one another. So what has happened since? We have an update!
